pages.transcription:
Osawatonie Ks. May 17/88
Anna Dear;
I want to tell you something in your ear! I think it is about time to mention it, as much things don't happen every day. I have an admirer here in Kansas! What do you think of that? I am told that I am "pretty"!? and sweet! and nice! So nice and sweet looking! Improved and improving! and I don't know what else. Are you not afraid it will spoil your unclear little sister? and make her vain & unnameable and all that and a unclear? Well, I manage to live along and take it all in, and really don't feel much later, but try to be better to please my loved one who loves me so much
